data.description: Pictures to come! Fully remodeled in 2020 with new electrical, new high efficiency furnace & air conditioning, radon mitigation system, new flooring, new granite counter tops, cabinets in kitchen, updated baths, new appliances, new paint inside and out including garage, new trim inside entire home. New storm doors installed on all 3 exterior doors. 2 bedrooms and full bath upstairs and in basement, complete with easement windows! Huge living space in basement! Metal roof! Back yard fenced with sitting/fire pit area, newer garage door, storage area in garage! Don't miss this Move in ready home! Close to shopping, dining and recreation!
